ast.name: Mandelbrot
ast.comment: Explore the Mandelbrot fractal by touch and save beautiful images on your phone that can be used as wallpaper for example.

decls.name: curry
decls.comment: current line in y we are drawing

decls.name: maxit
decls.comment: maximum iterations for a pixel. this increases with zoom.

decls.name: currx
decls.comment: current screen x coord we are drawing

decls.name: zoom-rate
decls.comment: the zoom rate at which we Zoom in when tapping

decls.name: lim-y
decls.comment: abs limit in y not to render dull parts of the set

decls.name: numcolblocks
decls.comment: number of ranges or blocks of colour in the palette

decls.name: colsinblock
decls.comment: num steps of colours in a block in the palette

decls.name: mag
decls.comment: current magnification level - changing this has no effect it is for info only.
